{
  "text": "where D m was the maximum displacement of the bead after the ARF impulse, S was material stiffness, and PRF was the pulse repetition frequency of the material [CITATION_1] . Reducing the PRF resulted in a linear reduction in the bead displacements, consistent with theory (Eq 8).",
